{"tid":1307173,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"撞日期又有咩好怕？ 7.28 將軍澳港島西聯合","createTime":"2019-07-11T12:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T11:57:21.000Z","uid":277191,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ffdfec11405877f1959840acafad700622f45c","tid":1307173,"uid":277191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地要遍地開花<br />\n等緊民陣公佈嘅同時幫手推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wnZBEQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wnZBEQ.png&h=f4a7ff4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.28 將軍澳港島西聯合大遊行之聲明<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳有染紅媒體，作不實報導抹黑示威者；西環有中聯辦，暗渡陳倉操控香港。<br />\n<br />\n兩區遊行召集人經協調後初步作出以下遊行時間之更改：<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳：1時30分集合，2時30分出發<br />\n港島西：4時集合，4時30分出發<br />\n（不反對通知書申請中，確實時間有待公佈）<br />\n<br />\n兩區經過商議後，了解雙方各自有調動日期之難處，為此遊行日期將維持於7.28，還望各方諒解。<br />\n<br />\n18區遍地開花，理應共同合作，目標一致為五大訴求而努力。7.28誠邀各位香港人先到將軍澳抗紅媒，後到西環探中聯辦，由東到西，將我們爭取民主、公義的聲音響遍香港！<br />\n<br />\n7.28 將軍澳港島西聯合大遊行召集人上"},{"pid":"ded43ad0c4bf5b10b9d3da4e120d7509fe4b8237","tid":1307173,"uid":277191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12cb57b683bd6bf775017520d3d63ac0707c858","tid":1307173,"uid":277191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f23b78297951a858fad9e08ea58e75bc62d0fd","tid":1307173,"uid":277191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f